To reduce pdf size -> pdf24 and ilovepdf (https://tools.pdf24.org/en/)
To extend pdf size as much as i need -> pdf pi7 (https://pdf.pi7.org/)
To edit pdf -> pdf escape and pdf24 (https://www.pdfescape.com/)

Alternate
1. To edit pdf -> pdf escape and pdf24 (https://www.pdfescape.com/)
2. (https://www.ilovepdf.com/compress_pdf)
3. (https://pdf.pi7.org/increase-pdf-size)
